# ============================================================================
# 8. DEPENDENCY LOCK FILES (Choose Strategy)
# ============================================================================

# OPTION A: COMMIT lock files for reproducibility (RECOMMENDED for production)
# Uncomment if using Yarn:
# !yarn.lock

# Uncomment if using pnpm:
# !pnpm-lock.yaml

# Uncomment if using npm:
# !package-lock.json

# OPTION B: Ignore all lock files (not recommended for production)
# yarn.lock
# pnpm-lock.yaml
# package-lock.json

